elements.name: Check Incoming Voice Call status API

steps.name: I set api with URL "twilio"
I add service "call_status" with URL and replace "account,sid" to set API endpoint
I get authentication username "username" and password "password" for API authentication
I hit "JSON GET" api with API endpoint and request body
I save response status to variable "Response_status" and response body to variable "Response_body"
I verify value of "Response_status" to be "200"
I validate response tag "status" with value "in-progress"
I click on "accept_call"
I force a sleep for "10" seconds
A different agent logs in
I force a sleep for "3" seconds
I wait for "transfer_call"
I click on "transfer_call"
I wait for "agents"
I mouse hover on "demo_agent"
I wait for "transfer_to_agent"
I click on "transfer_to_agent"
I wait for "complete_call"
I force a sleep for "3" seconds
I click on "complete_call"
I force a sleep for "3" seconds
I close all browsers
The call is accepted by the agent
